Deploy the profile \fIstage\fR:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

bake deploy stage
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
Deploy the profiles \fItest\fR, \fIstage\fR and \fIproduction\fR:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

bake deploy test stage production
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
