Bundle the default profile:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

bake deploy \-\-bundle
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
Bundle all profiles:
.
.IP "" 4
.
.nf

bake deploy \-\-all \-\-bundle
.
.fi
.
.IP "" 0
.
